## Summary
This documentation defines TypeScript type aliases for the progressive-profiling-shared plugin, including FormField with 13 supported field types (string, email, select, multiselect, etc.), FormSection with completion tracking, and ProfileFormData for structured form submissions.

## Keywords
- progressive-profiling-shared
- FormField type alias
- FormFieldValue union type
- FormSection type
- ProfileFormData array type
- TypeScript type definitions
- supertokens-plugins
- form field types (string, text, number, boolean, email, phone, date, select, multiselect, password, url, image-url, toggle)
- field validation (required, defaultValue, options)
- section completion tracking
- fieldId and sectionId mapping